      },
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023R2 is operated under the institution's ISO 9001:2015 QMS. A 27-case regression suite covering laminar, turbulent, and non-Newtonian benchmark problems is maintained in a Git repository (commit hash logged per run). Achieved level 3 reflects documented traceability beyond the MRL 3 minimum of level 2."
