        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "Solver error: round-off and iterative error contributions < 0.1% of discretization error",
        "description": "Round-off and iterative convergence errors must each contribute less than 0.1% of the total numerical error budget, verified by double-precision arithmetic checks and residual monitoring. The solver must not exhibit non-physical oscillations in the QoI time history."
      },
      "rationale": "All runs performed in double precision (64-bit). Round-off error estimated at < 10⁻¹² relative to QoI magnitude. Iterative error at final convergence (residual 8×10⁻⁷) contributes < 0.05% of the GCI-estimated discretization error. No non-physical pressure oscillations observed in time-history monitoring. Required and achieved levels both at 2."
    },
